metadata.name: Voyeur
metadata.description:
Voyeur

Observing, motionless
The body at rest
The mind mercurial

A hushed visual feast 
Completely at odds
With deafening insight

The spirit seeks quietude
The mind prowls for answers
The Seeker is alert


An Orbán Isma x Javier Maldoror Collaboration
A digital collage of real body suspension and daguerrotype aesthetics, exploring the occvlt through human experience.

This collaboration between Orbán Isma and Javier Maldoror presents a divination deck, exploring occult themes through the real experiences of those undergoing the experience of body suspension.
